{
  "texts": [
    "The results from other approaches show similar patterns to the observations discussed below.",
    "The details can be found in the supplement (see Supplemental Section 4).",
    "Overall, the importance metrics measured through the two computational algorithms were highly correlated in the positive direction with the negative WIS (Figure 6).",
    "That is, on average, the more accurate a model was by -WIS, the more important a role it played in contributing to the accuracy of an ensemble.",
    "In certain instances, the rankings of models by -WIS or importance metrics were not the same."
  ]
}